classroom instruction on student instructional days (as described in
IC 20-30-2-2) for a school year as required under IC 20-30-2-3, a
school corporation shall provide written notice to the department
regarding the date that the covered school building has ceased or will
cease being used for classroom instruction as described in this
subsection.".
